Depends: ${misc:Depends}, secubox-core (>= 1.0.0)
Recommends: crowdsec, secubox-crowdsec, secubox-haproxy
Description: SecuBox Web Application Firewall
 Mitmproxy-based threat detection with CrowdSec integration.
 .
 Features:
  - 300+ threat detection rules across 14+ categories
  - SQL injection, XSS, RCE, LFI detection
  - VoIP/SIP and XMPP attack detection
  - Router botnet and CVE exploit detection
  - Auto-ban with configurable sensitivity
  - Rate limiting per IP
  - CrowdSec integration for centralized banning
  - HAProxy reverse proxy integration
